      <title>中国股市最新消息：随着交易恢复，“国家队”已重返工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-20/china-s-national-team-is-back-at-work-as-trading-resumes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国一些跟踪中国股市的交易所交易基金在农历新年假期后的第一个交易日出现成交量激增。这可能表明国家支持的基金或所谓的国家队继续支持市场。夏洛特·杨 (Charlotte Yang) 在彭博电视台 (Bloomberg Television) 上有更多报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-20/china-s-national-team-is-back-at-work-as-trading-resumes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 02:18:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市监管机构誓言倾听市场呼声甚至批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-stock-watchdog-vows-to-heed-market-calls-even-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国证监会表示，将听取市场参与者的所有建议甚至批评，并及时解决他们的担忧，这一罕见的举动突显了其支撑中国8.6万亿美元股市的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/china-stock-watchdog-vows-to-heed-market-calls-even-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本创纪录利润显示日经指数有望创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/record-japan-profits-show-nikkei-is-primed-for-all-time-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本企业在截至 12 月的三个月中创下了创纪录的季度利润，支撑日经 225 指数上涨至接近历史峰值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/record-japan-profits-show-nikkei-is-primed-for-all-time-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:40:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡航展最新动态：失去航线、可持续燃料成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/singapore-air-show-latest-lost-routes-sustainable-fuel-a-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飞机交付延误、到 2050 年实现绿色环保的艰苦斗争以及机票价格的上涨使得乘坐飞机越来越成为富人的领域——本周，来自 1,000 多家公司的高管齐聚新加坡，参加亚洲最具影响力的航空航天和国防展览会，所有这些主题以及更多主题都将成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/singapore-air-show-latest-lost-routes-sustainable-fuel-a-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自 3 月份以来，Segantii 对冲基金资产缩水 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/segantii-hedge-fund-assets-shrank-by-1-billion-since-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，西蒙·萨德勒 (Simon Sadler) 的 Segantii Capital Management Ltd. 自去年 3 月以来，由于投资损失和赎回，其对冲基金资产缩水了 18%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/segantii-hedge-fund-assets-shrank-by-1-billion-since-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国银行将抵押贷款参考利率降幅创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/chinese-banks-cut-mortgage-reference-rate-by-most-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的银行将抵押贷款的关键参考利率下调了创纪录的幅度，这表明中国正在加大对房地产行业的支持力度，以重振需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/chinese-banks-cut-mortgage-reference-rate-by-most-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:21:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Star暴跌 悉尼赌场牌照可能被吊销</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/star-plunges-on-risk-sydney-casino-license-may-be-stripped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，新南威尔士州博彩监管机构发起第二次调查后，星娱乐集团有限公司股价跌至历史新低，这家陷入困境的公司可能会被剥夺悉尼旗舰赌场的经营许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/star-plunges-on-risk-sydney-casino-license-may-be-stripped</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 01:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>再次红海袭击后油价维持近三个月高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在胡塞武装再次袭击红海后，油价保持在三个多月来的最高水平附近，原油生产和贸易关键地区的紧张局势持续发酵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 23:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市周一逆转涨幅，泰铢下滑：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于抵押贷款参考利率的降低未能提振市场情绪，中国股市在亚洲股市原本平静的一天中下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 22:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>矿业巨头必和必拓认为，随着净利润下滑，镍市场的痛苦挥之不去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/bhp-s-first-half-profit-steady-as-inflation-lower-prices-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司(BHP Group Ltd.)上半年净利润较上年同期下降86%，此前镍市场供应过剩迫使这家全球最大矿商减记了关键资产的价值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/bhp-s-first-half-profit-steady-as-inflation-lower-prices-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 21:30:16 GMT</pubDate>
